This paper is about creating digital musical instruments using predictive neural network models. It involves the use of machine learning techniques to predict future control data from the user and precise temporal information. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.SD (Sound), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
